BEGIN_PGML
Evaluate the limit, [``\lim_{x\to 0}[$f]``], using either l'Hopital's rule or previously learned methods.



[``\lim_{x\to 0}[$f]=``][_______________]{$ans } (Enter a number,  `\infty,-\infty,`  or "DNE".) [@ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") @]*


END_PGML
